marketing: Shell Spirax S6 ATF A295 Oil is a fully synthetic, heavy-duty automatic transmission fluid which is specifically designed and approved for use in transmissions requiring Allison TES-295 fluids. Spirax S6 ATF A295 is approved for extended service intervals and remains stable even under severe operating conditions.
